4 Tathā, svakīyaṃ netṛṃ prati vṛttyā,
5 sā vastur mama prati gātum ārabdhā,
6 yasya upari dve jyotisī adṛśyete;

19 "Mama avibhraṃśa-buddhy-anugatena matena,
20 Yathā nyāyyā pratikriyā nyāyyena
21 Daṇḍitā syāt, tat-tvaṃ cittasthitam cakāra;

22 Ahaṃ tu tava cittaṃ śīghram eva vimokṣayiṣyāmi;
23 Tvaṃ ca śṛṇu, mama vacāṃsi
24 Mahān arthavādopadeśam tava pratipādayiṣyanti.

25 Na duḥkham anubhavetum śaknoti sa yaḥ puruṣaḥ
26 svārthe niyantraṇam icchati sa guṇasya,
27 sa ātmanā saha sarvām api svakīyām santatim nindati;

34 Atha vakṣyamāṇasya mukham āvartaya:
35 ayam prakṛtiḥ svakartṛṇā saha yuktā,
36 yathā sṛṣṭā, tathā niṣkalankaivā āsīt;

40 Tasmāt, ya śokaḥ śūlena dattaḥ,
41 yadi svīkṛtāyai prakṛtaye pramāṇīkṛtaḥ,
42 na kadācit kiṃcid evaṃ nyāyyena mṛtam;

46 Parantu ekena karmanā viśiṣṭāni phalāni sambhavanti:
47 yataḥ eka eva mṛtyuḥ Devāya ca Yahuḍīyebhyaś ca priyaḥ āsīt;
48 tasya nimittam pṛthivī kampitā āsīt, svargaś ca vivṛtaḥ āsīt.

55 Tvam vadasi: "Suṣṭhu vijānāmi yad aham śṛṇomi;
56 kimartham tu Bhagavān icchat, mama guhyam asti,
57 asmākam mokṣāya, api anena prakāreṇa".

73 Yāvadadhikam anurūpaṃ tadbhavati, tāvadadhikam tasyāḥ priyam bhavati;
74 yataḥ sarvameva prakāśayann pavitraḥ tejaḥ,
75 tadrūpatameva adhikam jvalati.

79 Pāpameva tad yad enam apahārayati
80 ca paraṃ śubhāt kṛtvā viṣamaṃ karoti,
81 yasmāt tasya prakāśasya alpam eva śuklatām āpnoti;

85 Tava prakṛtiḥ, yadā papāta sarvatra
86 tasya bīje, etad-guṇebhyaḥ,
87 yathā svargāt, parihṛtā abhūt;

100 yāvat anugṛhītavān icchati gantum ūrdhvam;
101 ayam ca ayam eva hetuḥ yasya naraḥ ātmanaḥ
102 tṛptim āpnotum artham svayam udyataḥ abhūt.

115 Yataḥ adhikaḥ āsīt Devaḥ ātmanam dātum
116 Naraṃ kṛtum samarthamabhyudgamāya,
117 Yat kimcid eva tasya tyaktena syāt;

124 Tvam vadasi: “Aham paśyāmi jalaṃ, aham paśyāmi agnim,
125 vāyuṃ ca pṛthivīṃ ca sarvāśca tāsāṃ saṃsthānāni
126 āgacchanti kṣayam, sthāyanti ca alpam kālam;

127 ime ca vastūni satyaṃ sṛṣṭāni āsīt;
128 tasmāt, yadi yat uktaṃ satyam abhūt,
129 tathāpi taiḥ kṣayāt rakṣaṇīyaṃ syāt”.

130 Devāḥ, bhrātar, eva viśuddhaśca deśaḥ
131 yasmin tvam asi, vaktuṃ śakyante sṛṣṭāḥ,
132 yathā santi, teṣāṃ pūrṇe bhāve;

139 Sarvasya paśoḥ pādapānāṃ ca ātmā
140 Sampūrṇasya prakṛter ākarṣati
141 Tejasvinām dīpānāṃ raśmim ca gatiṃ ca;
